public class TextTransfer
extends ByteArrayTransfer

Untamed: The class TextTransfer provides a platform specific mechanism for converting plain text represented as a java String to a platform specific representation of the data and vice versa. See Transfer for additional information.

An example of a java String containing plain text is shown below:

     String textData = "Hello World";
